parcel.name: Tezos Eco Gallery
parcel.label: gallery
parcel.description: Art gallery on the Tezos blockchain. Collection from: https://hicetnunc.xyz/tz/tz1c2iwyckUCcicx2qxqtwLEartYFEHg1pvB

features.text:
Welcome to the Tezos eco-friendly art gallery. 

All pieces you see on the walls belong to Ricky (https://twitter.com/Esclaponr). Everything here was sold on the website hicetnunc.xyz which is an NFT art exchange launched around the beginning of March 2021. hicetnunc runs on the Tezos cryptocurrency, which has no enviornmental cost associated with transactions because of the Proof of Stake design, and also means users don't need to pay large fees that are currently associated with transacting on Ehtereum. The fees per transaction on Tezos are less than $0.1 and won't increase based of demand.
